--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CONCEPT <AbcPane>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INTENTION
This concept describes the layout component 'AbcPane'.

The component serves as a presentation container for keywords that start with a
specific letter.
For example if the letter 'A' is associated with the container, then all keywords
begin with the letter 'A' or 'a'.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SPECIFICATION
 - Name      : AbcPane
 - Package   : org.naoghuman.lib.control.scene.layout.AbcPane
 - Structure : The structure of the component is an HBox container with a Label
               for the letter on the upper left side, while on the right side a
               FlowPane is positioned.
 - Additional: The developer has access to all three JavaFX components. This
               makes it possible, among other things, to adapt the style sheet
               of the components (colors, borders, effects) with CSS.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
EXAMPLE

class AbcPane {
  HBox     container;
  Label    letter;
  FlowPane keywords;
  ...
}

